Zachary Kapono Wilson (amụrụ n'August 3, 1999) bụ onye America na-agba bọọlụ quarterback maka New York Jets nke National Football League (NFL)
Ọ gbara bọọlụ kọleji na BYU, ebe ọ bụ MVP egwuregwu iko ugboro abụọ, ndị Jets họpụtara ya nke abụọ n'ozuzu ya na 2021 NFL Draft.
A mụrụ Wilson na Draper, Utah, na August 3, 1999
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Corner Canyon, ebe ọ gbara bọọlụ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị
Ọ gafere maka yad 2,986 na mmetụ aka 24 ka ọ na-agbakwa ọsọ maka yad 752 na aka asatọ dị ka onye isi
Wilson kwenyesiri ike na ọ ga-egwu nkeji iri na ise na Mahadum Boise State tupu ya emechaa kwụsị na ịhọrọ ịga Mahadum Brigham Young (BYU).
